ent.<\/li>\n<li>Ensures the implementation of the institutional affirmative action plan.<\/li>\n<\/ol>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<form id=\"adminForm\" action=\"https:\/\/www.parliament.na\/index.php\/directorates-nat-council\/national-council-office-of-the-secretary-to-the-national-council\" method=\"post\" name=\"adminForm\"><\/form>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text]<div id=\"ultimate-heading-55296849818c40e08\" class=\"uvc-heading ult-adjust-bottom-margin ultimate-heading-55296849818c40e08 uvc-6300 h2_bg_background uvc-heading-default-font-sizes\" data-hspacer=\"no_spacer\"  data-halign=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center\"><div class=\"uvc-heading-spacer no_spacer\" style=\"top\"><\/div><div class=\"uvc-main-heading ult-responsive\"  data-ultimate-target='.uvc-heading.ultimate-heading-55296849818c40e08 h2'  data-responsive-json-new='{\"font-size\":\"\",\"line-height\":\"\"}' ><h2 style=\"--font-weight:theme;\">Meet the Team Leaders<\/h2><\/div><\/div><style type=\"text\/css\" data-type=\"the7_shortcodes-inline-css\">.dt-team-shortcode.team-masonry-shortcode-id-39526db0dcdb908f47fd3e3ac6570693 .team-desc {\n  padding: 20px 20px 20px 20px;\n}\n.dt-team-shortcode.team-masonry-shortcode-id-39526db0dcdb908f47fd3e3ac6570693 .team-author-name,\n.dt-team-shortcode.team-masonry-shortcode-id-39526db0dcdb908f47fd3e3ac6570693 .team-author-name a {\n  margin-bottom: 0px;\n  font-weight: bold;\n}\n.dt-team-shortcode.team-masonry-shortcode-id-39526db0dcdb908f47fd3e3ac6570693 .team-author p {\n  margin-bottom: 10px;\n  font-style: italic;\n}\n.dt-team-shortcode.team-masonry-shortcode-id-39526db0dcdb908f47fd3e3ac6570693  .team-media {\n  padding: 0px 0px 0px 0px;\n}\n.dt-team-shortcode.team-masonry-shortcode-id-39526db0dcdb908f47fd3e3ac6570693 .dt-css-grid .team-media img {\n  max-width: 100%;\n}\n.dt-team-shortcode.team-masonry-shortcode-id-39526db0dcdb908f47fd3e3ac6570693 .team-content {\n  margin-bottom: 5px;\n}\n.dt-team-shortcode.team-masonry-shortcode-id-39526db0dcdb908f47fd3e3ac6570693  .